cbc presents the stratford festival is a canadian film and television series . produced by the stratford festival in conjunction with cbc television , the series aims to film a stratford production of every william shakespeare play by 2025 . in addition to airing on cbc television , the films will also be distributed theatrically both in and outside of canada . the project received a $ 3 million grant from the federal economic development agency for southern ontario in july 2015 .